name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
display-name: Vellum Client API
environments:
  Production:
    urls:
      Default: https://api.vellum.ai
      Predict: https://predict.vellum.ai
      Documents: https://documents.vellum.ai
default-environment: Production
auth-schemes:
  apiKeyAuth:
    header: X_API_KEY
    name: apiKey
    type: string
auth: apiKeyAuth
